name: Tic Tac Toe
body:
It is a simple Tic-Tac-Toe game and you can play with the computer too! The computer has two AI-Players, having two levels of smartness. It is almost impossible to beat the hard level :sunglasses:. The game was first created [in C](https://github.com/MinhasKamal/CoolConsoleGames/blob/master/src/CrissCrossV-2.c), then was rewritten and converted to Java. The actual name of the project was **CrissCross**. ### License
